  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   E = mc²
Formula: E = mc²
Note:    Mass-energy equivalence; foundation of nuclear physics

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Pythagorean Theorem
Formula: a² + b² = c²
Note:    Right triangle relationship; foundation of geometry

Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Age of Universe
Formula: 13.8 billion years
Note:    Determined by CMB and Hubble constant measurement

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Gravitational Force
Formula: F = Gm1m2/r²
Note:    Universal gravitation between all masses

Domain:  Geology
Topic:   Age of Earth
Formula: 4.54 billion years
Note:    Determined by radiometric dating of oldest rocks/meteorites

